message: "If Agent Trust Lab helps your work, please cite it using the metadata below."
title: "Agent Trust Lab: Human-in-the-Loop Trust Reports for Risk-Sensitive LLM Outputs"
version: "0.1.0"
date-released: "2026-06-09"
type: software
authors:
  - family-names: "Guo"
    given-names: "Zhaojie"
repository-code: "https://github.com/benben951/agent-trust-lab"
url: "https://benben951.github.io/agent-trust-lab/"
abstract: >-
  Agent Trust Lab is a public-safe prototype for generating structured trust
  reports for risk-sensitive LLM and agent outputs. It includes synthetic review
  cases, deterministic findings, Markdown and JSON reports, baseline comparison,
  metrics summaries, and human-in-the-loop routing recommendations.
keywords:
  - llm-evaluation
  - agent-evaluation
  - trust-and-safety
  - human-in-the-loop
  - aml
  - compliance
  - risk-review
